reviewText: I have loved this movie ever since I was a little girl. I am so glad to have found it.

Great movie. I don't regret buying it! It's just how I remember it!! MUST BUY IT'S AN AMAing story with great songs! (: If you love Gloria trevi then you will love this movie!!! FUNNY and will keep you laughing!!

-ARMY WIFEYAND ALEXIS MAMA
